org.hkijena.jipipe.api.data

Interface JIPipeDataDisplayOperation

  • All Superinterfaces:
    JIPipeDataOperation
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AddROIToActiveJIPipeImageViewerDataDisplay, AddROIToJIPipeImageViewerDataDisplay, AddToROIManagerDataDisplay, CacheAwareOpenResultsTableInJIPipeDataOperation, CopyPathDataOperation, DefaultDataDisplayOperation, ImportImageJPathDataOperation, ImportJIPipeProjectDataOperation, OpenInImageJDataDisplay, OpenPathDataOperation, OpenPlotInJIPipeDataOperation, OpenResultsTableInImageJDataOperation, OpenResultsTableInJIPipeTabDataOperation, OpenTextInJIPipeDataOperation

    public interface JIPipeDataDisplayOperation
extends JIPipeDataOperation
    An operation that is executed on showing existing data located in memory/cache. This acts as additional entry in the cache browser display menu. Must be registered.
